data.description: Step into the warmth and comfort of this charming residence nestled in the serene Annecy neighborhood of Matthews, North Carolina. Step inside to discover a foyer with high ceilings, setting a welcoming tone for the rest of the home. With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, including a cozy office space with French doors, there's plenty of room for the whole family to enjoy. The primary suite beckons with its spacious layout and a beautifully appointed bathroom featuring a glass shower and standalone bathtub. The heart of the home lies in the sparkling white kitchen, complete with a wine fridge built into the center island. Relax in the cozy living room, where a wood-burning fireplace creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. Outside, the expansive backyard offers plenty of space for outdoor activities and gatherings, making it the perfect place to unwind and enjoy the beauty of nature. This home also features a voice-controlled Smart thermostat for added convenience. Welcome home to Annecy.
